# Native quackwire JNI shim - local CMake build tree.
# Per-platform `libquackwire.{so,dylib}` binaries live in a GitHub Release
# (built by `.github/workflows/quackwire.yml`) and are fetched into
# `target/.../resource_managed/main/native/<platform>/` by the
# `QuackwireArtifact.fetchQuackwire` sbt task at compile time, so the
# source tree never carries them.
native/quackwire/build*/

# Locally-built libquackwire binaries. The sbt resource generator
# `QuackwireArtifact.fetchQuackwire` may fall back to them, but they are
# developer-machine artifacts; CI fetches the official set from the
# GitHub Release into `target/.../resource_managed/`.
src/main/resources/native/
